Key Match Events: The game was tied 6-6 in the bottom of the 9th inning before Nick Castellanos' single won it for the Phillies.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The game was part of the NLDS, with the series tied 1-1.The attendance at Citizens Bank Park was 45,679.
Others: Umpires included Edwin Moscoso, Doug Eddings, James Hoye, Carlos Torres, Rob Drake, and Andy Fletcher.
